{"tid":2436071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清算港台︱李百全表明「最着重黃藍」 疑向《鏗鏘集》埋手","createTime":"2021-03-06T19:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T03:40:30.000Z","uid":126919,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"858c108470c23fef3ed378ec47636e11ad60c439","tid":2436071,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T19:35:58.000Z","msg":"零傳媒經驗的廣播處長李百全空降數天即亮劍，港台電視部公共事務組節目《香港故事》成「第一滴血」，李百全周四（4日）編輯會議上批評《香港故事》訪問樂隊LMF「唔decent（正經）」後，《蘋果》獲悉，李事後疑沒有看過該集的訪問，已決定抽起該集，改播舊節目；同節目即將播出探討讀書文化等集數，李也沒有看過就決定抽起。據了解，當日李更在會上表明自己：「最着重黃藍」。<br />\n港台晚上回覆時未有正面回應，僅稱港台必須恪守《約章》及《節目製作人員守則》，又指廣播處長在具爭議性的節目播出前會「檢視」，保障節目符合約章及守則要求。消息人士指，《香港故事》已是最「溫和」紀錄片，亦算是「易下手」的節目：「如果呢個做法（DQ）喺《香港故事》OK，咁《鏗鏘集》都OK。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210306/LYXBXH2OYNERFC5UMVGOE6JOTU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210306%2FLYXBXH2OYNERFC5UMVGOE6JOTU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bOoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=894353c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210306%2FLYXBXH2OYNERFC5UMVGOE6JOTU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=018e7aed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210306/LYXBXH2OYNERFC5UMVGOE6JOTU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"ac363aba9a64693a4a8cfb14f7201057b26966f1","tid":2436071,"uid":126919,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T19:39:33.000Z","msg":"廣播處長李百全周四編輯會議上要求，即日起公共事務組播出的節目須經他過目，其中《香港故事》將播出樂隊LMF的訪問，被他斥LMF唱「充滿器官」的粗口歌，有極端政治取態，更反問「點解唔搵曹永廉做訪問？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b60da8908fbc2f220c7ea6c2fc8288229ed06c","tid":2436071,"uid":126919,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T19:40:05.000Z","msg":"執柒咗佢算啦"},{"pid":"4f664662849c77edf6922f823be4e2d5a85e7242","tid":2436071,"uid":42804,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T19:43:15.000Z","msg":"鏟除香港文化，為引入中國文化，讓中國文化侵蝕現有香港嘅一切<br />\n不出多久，後生嘅只會知道香港係中國嘅一部分。"},{"pid":"d2d16aee58750474df9a3f4b403d5ed0d1816aab","tid":2436071,"uid":42804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"94b60da8908fbc2f220c7ea6c2fc8288229ed06c","tid":2436071,"uid":126919,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T19:40:05.000Z","msg":"執柒咗佢算啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T19:44:03.000Z","msg":"政治任務<br />\n邊會執？"},{"pid":"3c1ff2a5a967e4dea62a30fab9d5800be5a132cb","tid":2436071,"uid":42804,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ac363aba9a64693a4a8cfb14f7201057b26966f1","tid":2436071,"uid":126919,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T19:39:33.000Z","msg":"廣播處長李百全周四編輯會議上要求，即日起公共事務組播出的節目須經他過目，其中《香港故事》將播出樂隊LMF的訪問，被他斥LMF唱「充滿器官」的粗口歌，有極端政治取態，更反問「點解唔搵曹永廉做訪問？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T19:46:52.000Z","msg":"只係藉口<br />\n唔係因為粗口歌意識不良嘅問題<br />\n而係因為Lmf一向標榜反極權，有違「愛國者治港」原則"},{"pid":"63403a9739835889e5824ae415db23476384efd9","tid":2436071,"uid":312859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94b60da8908fbc2f220c7ea6c2fc8288229ed06c","tid":2436071,"uid":126919,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T19:40:0